WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.430
- <i>Previously on</i> The Originals...
- We were in love for two centuries.

00:02.432 --> 00:04.723
- What the hell happened?
- I asked you to leave with me!

00:04.726 --> 00:06.955
But you didn't love me as
much as you love New Orleans.

00:06.957 --> 00:08.122
I saw things, Rebekah,

00:08.125 --> 00:10.592
<i>in his mind. Not just memories.</i>

00:10.594 --> 00:12.328
<i>I saw his natural instincts, and...</i>

00:12.330 --> 00:14.329
I think maybe that's who he really is.

00:14.331 --> 00:15.897
VINCENT: The Hollow is
stronger than we are.

00:15.899 --> 00:16.898
It's got more followers,

00:16.900 --> 00:18.499
<i>and it's gonna destroy New Orleans.</i>

00:18.501 --> 00:20.040
LEAD ACOLYTE:
The Hollow has shed her flesh

00:20.042 --> 00:21.436
to take on that of another.

00:21.438 --> 00:22.670
We'll kill that body as well.

00:22.672 --> 00:23.738
Oh, you won't dare.

00:23.740 --> 00:25.006
<i>Even now, she's locking herself</i>

00:25.008 --> 00:26.141
<i>within the greatest witch</i>

00:26.143 --> 00:27.467
<i>this world may ever know.</i>

00:27.470 --> 00:29.444
Hope's gone. She's the Hollow now.

00:29.446 --> 00:31.312
I have to find her.

00:31.314 --> 00:33.065
Vincent, surely you
can pull the Hollow out.

00:33.068 --> 00:35.316
- I think I know a way to save her.
- Anything.

00:35.318 --> 00:37.637
If we go this route, this is
gonna be the end of your family.

00:37.639 --> 00:40.254
This is gonna be the end
of always and forever.

00:41.358 --> 00:43.391
VINCENT: The Hollow has
been haunting New Orleans

00:43.393 --> 00:44.759
for centuries.

00:44.761 --> 00:47.194
It's an unending evil.

00:47.196 --> 00:49.979
Its appetite for power is insatiable.

00:49.982 --> 00:52.665
And that's what attracted
it to your little girl.

00:52.668 --> 00:54.281
You said there was a way to save her.

00:54.284 --> 00:55.222
VINCENT: There is.

00:55.225 --> 00:56.719
But I'm gonna tell you right now,

00:56.722 --> 00:58.522
you are not gonna like my plan.

00:59.575 --> 01:01.842
Step one:

01:01.844 --> 01:03.977
we pull the Hollow out of Hope.

01:03.979 --> 01:07.614
Step two: we find
someplace else to put it.

01:07.616 --> 01:09.716
But with the book gone, I need a place

01:09.718 --> 01:11.951
that's both powerful and eternal.

01:11.953 --> 01:13.987
And in order to make the
transition work, I'm gonna need

01:13.989 --> 01:15.995
something that's connected
to Hope through blood.

01:15.998 --> 01:17.824
You need a vampire.

01:18.894 --> 01:21.227
You want to put the Hollow
into one of my siblings.

01:21.229 --> 01:23.696
Uh, one ain't gonna cut it.

01:26.134 --> 01:28.101
I'm gonna need four of them.

01:29.837 --> 01:31.058
Why four of us?

01:31.061 --> 01:33.306
Well, 1,500 years ago, when
the Hollow was first killed,

01:33.308 --> 01:34.774
they divided her remains.

01:34.776 --> 01:36.342
Four bones, four volunteers,

01:36.344 --> 01:37.576
four different locations.

01:37.578 --> 01:39.879
That's how we're going
to beat the Hollow now.

01:41.080 --> 01:43.508
Transfer the Hollow's power
into four immortal vampires.

01:43.511 --> 01:45.284
And just send us on our way.

01:45.286 --> 01:46.459
So the evil is drawn,

01:46.462 --> 01:48.754
quartered and separated for all time.

01:48.756 --> 01:50.489
And you have to go your separate ways,

01:50.491 --> 01:51.857
and you have to stay separate.

01:51.859 --> 01:53.625
For all time.

01:53.627 --> 01:55.394
We can never see each other again.

01:56.230 --> 01:57.896
Can never go near each other again.

02:02.102 --> 02:04.669
That is the only way that
we're gonna beat the Hollow.

02:06.974 --> 02:10.908
Well, if it'll save my little
girl, then we will make it so.

